name: Nevertheless,
overview: The intoxicating charm of a flirtatious art school classmate pulls a reluctant love cynic into a friends-with-benefits relationship.
tagline: Love. I know that it will cause me pain again. Nevertheless, I still...

episodes.name: There’s No Such Thing as Fate. Nevertheless,
episodes.overview: Days after a heart-fluttering encounter with a charming man, Yu Na-bi bumps into him again. This time, she's formally introduced to Park Jae-eon.

episodes.name: It's Not Only Me. Nevertheless,
episodes.overview: As Na-bi wonders whether Jae-eon only acts friendly toward her or also to other girls, she has a racy dream about the two of them in bed.

episodes.name: It Has Already Begun. Nevertheless,
episodes.overview: A cold, some jealousy and a slight misunderstanding drive Na-bi and Jae-eon further apart before bringing them closer than ever before.

episodes.name: I Know It Isn't Love. Nevertheless,
episodes.overview: Na-bi's attraction to Jae-eon is enough to momentarily quiet her concerns about their intimate relationship — until a rude awakening sets in.

episodes.name: I Know Nothing Will Change. Nevertheless,
episodes.overview: Sick of Jae-eon's ways, Na-bi ends things with him. Oh Bit-na makes a drunken confession. Yun Seol-a approaches Na-bi on campus.

episodes.name: There's No Such Thing as Love. Nevertheless,
episodes.overview: Na-bi visits her hometown, where she helps out in her aunt's studio and enjoys the outdoors with Yang Do-hyeok. Jae-eon feels Na-bi's absence.

episodes.name: I Know There's No Turning Back. Nevertheless,
episodes.overview: The students arrive at the guesthouse for a group retreat. Na-bi tries to keep a distance from Jae-eon, who keeps his eye on her and Do-hyeok.

episodes.name: I Know It's a Lie. Nevertheless,
episodes.overview: Do-hyeok surprises his childhood crush with a sweet confession. Na-bi visits a gallery with Jae-eon. Yun Sol gets honest about her feelings for Seo Ji-wan.

episodes.name: I Know It's Over. Nevertheless,
episodes.overview: Afraid to lose Na-bi, Do-hyeok shows up in front of her building — only to see Jae-eon by her side. Sol allays Ji-wan's fears about their relationship.

episodes.name: Nevertheless, I Still…
episodes.overview: Na-bi scrambles to recreate her sculpture days before the exhibit. Staying true to his word, Jae-eon bids farewell to his butterflies.
